    <item>
      <title>刚果将 Tenke 的铜出售给三家重量级交易商</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/congo-sells-copper-from-tenke-to-trio-of-trading-heavyweights</link>
      <description><![CDATA[嘉能可公司 (Glencore Plc)、摩科瑞能源集团 (Mercuria Energy Group) 和托克集团 (Trafigura Group) 正在从刚果民主共和国的国有矿业公司购买铜，这是该公司首次销售来自合资项目的金属。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/congo-sells-copper-from-tenke-to-trio-of-trading-heavyweights</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗认为一些科技公司今年仍在考虑在美国上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/citi-sees-some-tech-companies-still-weighing-us-ipos-this-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗集团一位高级银行家表示，一些科技公司正考虑在今年最后三个月在美国交易所上市，这激发了潜在的 IPO 浪潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/citi-sees-some-tech-companies-still-weighing-us-ipos-this-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 17:16:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Blue Owl 加入债券热潮，发行 10 亿美元债券偿还债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/blue-owl-joins-debt-rush-with-bond-to-pay-down-credit-facilities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，Blue Owl Capital Inc. 的一只基金将在美国高等级债券市场出售 10 亿美元债券，延续过去几天新债券发行的强劲势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/blue-owl-joins-debt-rush-with-bond-to-pay-down-credit-facilities</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 16:09:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国开始出售德国商业银行股份，首席执行官宣布离职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/commerzbank-ceo-flags-departure-as-germany-starts-to-sell-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国商业银行首席执行官曼弗雷德·诺夫 (Manfred Knof) 不会寻求延长合同，这使得该德国银行在政府开始出售其股份的同时寻找替代者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/commerzbank-ceo-flags-departure-as-germany-starts-to-sell-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 16:04:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
